6Oth475/NFsGCQ2q74WOWQ==.text: The ultimate goal of {=KOCHKA Café} is to help cats who really need it. Having a coffee shop definitely helps. However, we would like to give an extraordinary life to our cats. Why? Because all of our cats went through some bad times in their life. Either they were abandoned, thrown away, or born into some bad conditions. And we believe that all of them deserve to have the best - the ultimate second chance.

t.text: How do we admit new cats to KOCHKA Café?

HNj6uP7iL4RwLwCN8j5QxQ==.text: Each cat goes through a quarantine that lasts a minimum of 14 days. During this period we give them necessary medical care, deworming, recommended vaccination, and sterilization (in case their age allows that). Only after that, the cats can enter our café and can be adopted.

t.text: Each cat goes through a quarantine that lasts a minimum of 14 days. During this period we give them necessary medical care, deworming, recommended vaccination, and sterilization (in case their age allows that). Only after that, the cats can enter our café and can be adopted.

vWCRUi4GIhnx8ENyPDWUzA==.text: Older cats go through the same process except they already have to be sterilized before we can accept them. We cannot accept adult cats that are not sterilized.

t.text: Older cats go through the same process except they already have to be sterilized before we can accept them. We cannot accept adult cats that are not sterilized.

t.text: How can you adopt a new cat?

6u2zOP6qUybHiM6neM/GuA==.text: We try to create an environment supporting reasonable adoptions only. Every person who wants to adopt a cat has to fill a questionnaire to make sure our cats will find a safe and loving home. We also conduct an interview and ask for a financial contribution to cover part of the costs connected with the cats' medical treatment.

t.text: We try to create an environment supporting reasonable adoptions only. Every person who wants to adopt a cat has to fill a questionnaire to make sure our cats will find a safe and loving home. We also conduct an interview and ask for a financial contribution to cover part of the costs connected with the cats' medical treatment.

XiCuItUtGxqiz2oUqvDfew==.text: It is also necessary to visit us in person first to get familiar with our cats. It's not possible to adopt a cat from KOCHKA Café without visiting us first.

t.text: It is also necessary to visit us in person first to get familiar with our cats. It's not possible to adopt a cat from KOCHKA Café without visiting us first.
